Gerber Graduates Puffs Cereal Snack are easy to chew and swallow and are just the right size for little hands to pick up and enjoy.

  • For Crawlers (8+ Months)

  • 2g of Whole Grains Per Serving
  • Non-GMO
  • Kosher

products.romanceDescription:
HERSHEY'S Chocolate Syrup is an easy way to add delicious chocolate flavor to countless treats. This syrup is full of rich chocolaty flavor and is easy to squeeze or pour onto a dessert. It makes a tasty chocolate syrup for milk, or try using it as an easy and delectable ice cream topping. Not only is this fat free syrup full of rich chocolaty flavor, but it also has no gluten or artificial colors. HERSHEY'S Chocolate Syrup is sure to make dessert time better than ever. Packaged in an easy to use squeeze bottle, refrigerate after opening to maintain freshness.

• One bottle of HERSHEY'S Chocolate Syrup
• Perfect for topping ice cream sundaes or making tasty chocolate milk
• Packaged in an easy to use squeeze bottle
• Fat free and gluten free chocolate flavored syrup with no artificial flavors
• Versatile and full of rich chocolate flavor
• Top delicious birthday desserts or use to make hot cocoa on a cold day

products.description: Oreo Double Stuf Chocolate Sandwich Cookies
products.romanceDescription:
OREO Double Stuf Chocolate Sandwich Cookies have been America's favorite cookie for over 100 years. Stuffed with twice the OREO creme, these chocolate sandwich cookies are supremely dunkable. Double Stuf OREO cookies are great sweet snacks for sharing or enjoying with cold milk. The resealable package with easy-pull tab keeps chocolate cookies fresh and is perfect for snacking or traveling.

  • One 15.35 oz package of OREO Double Stuf Chocolate Sandwich Cookies
  • Chocolate wafers stuffed with twice the OREO creme
  • Sandwich cookies are perfectly dunkable
  • Enjoy as birthday treats or a sweet snack any day of the week

products.romanceDescription: Prego Traditional Pasta Sauce features the rich, sweet flavor of vine-ripened tomatoes balanced with savory herbs and seasonings. Simply pour over pasta or use this classic to transform pantry ingredients into plenty of family-pleasing recipes. Try this tomato sauce in your next spaghetti and meatballs, chicken parmesan, or bolognese for a new quick and easy take on your favorite dishes. Prego pasta sauces are made with savory herbs and seasonings you can taste in every bite.

products.description: Ben & Jerry's Half Baked Ice Cream
products.romanceDescription:
Ben & Jerry's is proud to partner with fellow B Corps Greyston & Rhino Bakeries to bring you half baked. The incredible stories behind both the fudge brownies & cookie dough make this a flavor that not only tastes good, but does good.

  • Chocolate & vanilla ice creams with fudge brownies & gobs of chocolate chip cookie dough
  • All of Ben & Jerry’s ice cream is made with non-GMO sourced ingredients & cage-free eggs
  • Ben & Jerry's ice cream includes Fairtrade certified cocoa, sugar, and vanilla
  • Ice cream with kosher certified dairy
  • Ben & Jerry's ice cream uses responsibly sourced packaging

products.description: (LMTD QTY) ChapStick Classic Cherry Lip Balm
products.romanceDescription: When it comes to caring for your lips, you can’t go wrong with a classic. ChapStick Classic Original is the one you know and love. It’s the lip protection you grew up with, that trusted tube you’ve turned to time after time. America’s favorite lip balm, ChapStick Classic Original for lips glides on easily to soften and protect delicate skin. Use as directed to help heal or prevent dry, chapped lips, and apply it daily to help keep lips silky smooth. Through every season, at home or on the go, trust ChapStick Classic Original lip balm for everyday comforting lip care.
